name: Chilmole | Spicy Black Soup
description: The Chilmole or Relleno negro is a dish of Yucatecan cuisine, based on turkey, black meatballs with a boiled egg in the center. What gives this broth its characteristic flavor is the black paste's condiments and spicy mixed peppers.
